This solution uses a while loop to continuously divide the input number `n` by 3 as long as it is divisible evenly (i.e., `n % 3 == 0`). If `n` is a power of three, this process will eventually reduce `n` to 1. If `n` is not a power of three, this process will leave a remainder greater than 1.

